a-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 01, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cip1719811789925.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cip1719811789925.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cip1719811789925.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ilf1665702634757\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n trigger createShortcutTo \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__trigger_createshortcutto_394081\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Interactive trigger that handles processing when one or more items are dropped on a tree or picture widget by a <code class=\"ph codeph\">Create Shortcut</code> drop action.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__topic_d117017e1_d117018e1_d117019e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104cip1719811789925_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__codeblock_pwn_wvk_xbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">   trigger createShortcutTo\n   params\n      string dragvalue : in\n      string dropformat : in\n      string itemvalue : in\n      numeric numberofobjects : in\n      numeric index : in\n   endparams\n   <var class=\"keyword varname\">; &lt;Your code here&gt;</var>\n   end ; trigger createShortcutTo\n         </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__section_w1196ab1b7b5_w1197ab1b7_w1198ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__table_d14444e1_d14445e1_d14446e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Applies to:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Form widgets: <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rgn1665702634165.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rgn1665702634165.html\" title=\"Image to use as the background image on the map widget.\">Image Name</a> , <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gge1665702634237.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" title=\"The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.\">utree (Tree)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Activation:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Activated on the target widget when a <code class=\"ph codeph\">Create Shortcut</code> drop action occurs, once for each source object.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Default behavior:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Behavior upon completion:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__topic_d83187e1_d83188e1_d83189e1_d83190e1_d83191e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d92694e168\">\n                       Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__d5924e22\"><span class=\"keyword parmname\">dragvalue</span>— value of the\n               dragged object. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__d5924e27\"><span class=\"keyword parmname\">dropformat</span>—negotiated drop\n               format. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__d5924e32\">\n<span class=\"keyword parmname\">itemvalue</span>—value of the\n\t\t (tree) item on which the drop occurs. If the drop occurs on a picture widget, the value will be\n\t\t <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"\"</code> (empty string). </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__d5924e42\">For multiple drops:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__d5924e47\"><span class=\"keyword parmname\">numberofobjects</span>—number of\n               multiple objects being dropped. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__d5924e52\"><span class=\"keyword parmname\">index</span>—numeric index,\n               starting with 1, of the object being dropped. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__topic_d83192e1_d83193e1_d83194e1_d83195e1_d83196e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d92694e212\">\n                       Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__d5925e20\">Tree and Picture widgets support drag and drop\n        behavior using drag-and-drop formats, which are global objects that define the actions,\n        pop-up menu, and cursor icons available when dragging or dropping objects in these widgets.\n        For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eav1719500059023.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eav1719500059023.html#mpv1665702633806__topic_d18247e1_d18248e1_d18249e1_d18250e1_d18251e1\">Drag and Drop Behavior for Tree and Picture Widgets</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ilf1665702634757__d5925e25\">If the ProcScript in the trigger returns\n\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code>, the associated object is not dropped. If it returns <code class=\"ph codeph\">-2</code>, the drop\n\t\taction is aborted for all objects.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ieb1705583991220.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Defining Drag and Drop Behavior for Picture and Tree Widgets</a><p>Drag and drop properties are supported by picture widgets and items in the tree widget.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swj1719500297780.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Drag-and-Drop Formats</a><p>Drag-and-drop formats are global objects that define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon that are available when performing drag and drop actions in the tree and picture widgets. They are not used for drag-and-drop widgets.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419952\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419952\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "trigger createShortcutTo Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 01, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 trigger createShortcutTo Interactive trigger that handles processing when one or more items are dropped on a tree or picture widget by a Create Shortcut drop action. Explain this code trigger createShortcutTo params string dragvalue : in string dropformat : in string itemvalue : in numeric numberofobjects : in numeric index : in endparams ; <Your code here> end ; trigger createShortcutTo Copy Applies to: Form widgets: Image Name , utree (Tree) Activation: Activated on the target widget when a Create Shortcut drop action occurs, once for each source object. Default behavior: None Behavior upon completion: None Parameters dragvalue — value of the dragged object. dropformat —negotiated drop format. itemvalue —value of the (tree) item on which the drop occurs. If the drop occurs on a picture widget, the value will be \"\" (empty string). For multiple drops: numberofobjects —number of multiple objects being dropped. index —numeric index, starting with 1, of the object being dropped. Description Tree and Picture widgets support drag and drop behavior using drag-and-drop formats, which are global objects that define the actions, pop-up menu, and cursor icons available when dragging or dropping objects in these widgets. For more information, see Drag and Drop Behavior for Tree and Picture Widgets . If the ProcScript in the trigger returns -1 , the associated object is not dropped. If it returns -2 , the drop action is aborted for all objects. Related Links Defining Drag and Drop Behavior for Picture and Tree Widgets Drag and drop properties are supported by picture widgets and items in the tree widget. Drag-and-Drop Formats Drag-and-drop formats are global objects that define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon that are available when performing drag and drop actions in the tree and picture widgets. They are not used for drag-and-drop widgets. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}